# Folder Structure

- Keep landlord/central concerns under `app/Landlord/*`.
- Keep shared primitives in `app/Modules/Shared/*`.
- Place use-case commands in `Application/Commands` and handlers in `Application/Handlers`.
- Keep framework wiring in `app/Providers`, HTTP endpoints in `routes/*` and controllers.
- Prefer adding new code in existing context folders over creating ad-hoc top-level directories.
- Mirror namespace to path exactly (PSR-4).
